com.almeros.android.multitouch

Interface ShoveGestureDetector.OnShoveGestureListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ShoveGestureDetector.SimpleOnShoveGestureListener
    Enclosing class:
    ShoveGestureDetector

    public static interface ShoveGestureDetector.OnShoveGestureListener
    Listener which must be implemented which is used by ShoveGestureDetector to perform callbacks to any implementing class which is registered to a ShoveGestureDetector via the constructor.
    See Also:
    ShoveGestureDetector.SimpleOnShoveGestureListener
